title: The Middleman v.1 # 1-4 (Viper Comics)
description:
Written by Javier Grillo-Marxuach
Illustrated by Les McClaine

Four issues published by Viper Comics 2005

Your reality is a sham. Your way of life is constantly under attack by monsters, aliens and talking primates. The reason you and the rest of the normal world doesn't know it; The Middleman. Working in absurd secrecy, aided by talented amateur Wendy Watson, the Middleman stares down threats extra-, infra-, and juxta-terrestrial with a big gun and a grin.
